Package com.cyc.baseclient.kbtool

Classes which wrap common operations for KB content, such as assertion, querying, etc; this code is not supported for external developers.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AssertToolImpl
    Tools for asserting facts to the Cyc KB.
    ComparisonToolImpl
    Tools for comparing different CycObjects.
    InferenceToolImpl
    Tools for performing inferences over the Cyc KB.
    InspectorToolImpl
    Tools for examining individual CycObjects.
    KbObjectToolImpl
    Provides tools for converting KbObjects to Base Client objects.
    KeTextToolImpl  
    LookupToolImpl
    Tools for looking up CycObjects in the Cyc KB.
    ObjectToolImpl
    Tools for creating simple CycObjects, such as constants and lists.

    RkfToolImpl Deprecated
    TemplateOeToolImpl  
    UnassertToolImpl
